Because most clients modify the standard printable forms to suit their needs, the customized report is not installed so as not to overwrite your modified report. You can choose to make the same or similar changes we made to the printable form (which the report provides) to your own form or if you have not made changes yet, install the customized version of the report and subreport and tailor them to your needs.{br}{TOC} ==Report Files== The printable form for quotes consists of the main <tt>SO641000.rpx</tt> report and the <tt>SO6411AM.rpx</tt> subreport. The modified version of the main report has the <tt>SO641000AM.rpx</tt> name and can be found in the <tt>site/ReportsDefault</tt> folder along with the subreport. ==How to Modify a Custom Quote Report=={br}
